{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":800,"text":"I spend most of my time"},{"time":4800,"text":"thinking about little girls,"},{"time":8280,"text":"which is kind of a weird thing\nfor a grown man in our society to say."},{"time":13080,"text":"But I do. I spend most of my time\nthinking about little girls,"},{"time":16040,"text":"and I think it's primarily\nbecause I have one."},{"time":19160,"text":"This one's mine, and I think\nyou would really like her."},{"time":22240,"text":"She is smart and funny"},{"time":24720,"text":"and kind to people and a good friend."},{"time":27960,"text":"But when I talk about my daughter,\nthe word I find myself saying most"},{"time":32360,"text":"is \"athlete.\""},{"time":34400,"text":"My kid's athletic."},{"time":36240,"text":"She is strong and fast"},{"time":38800,"text":"and has great balance\nand good body control."},{"time":42000,"text":"She is a three-time,\nback-to-back-to-back state champion"},{"time":45400,"text":"in Shaolin Kempo."},{"time":47080,"text":"At nine years old, she is already\nhalfway to a black belt."},{"time":50800,"text":"My daughter is athletic."}]},{"cues":[{"time":52600,"text":"Now, when a man who is six feet two\nand 265 pounds stands in front of you"},{"time":56800,"text":"and says his daughter is athletic,"},{"time":58560,"text":"you might think\nthat's a reflection of him."},{"time":60800,"text":"It is not."}]},{"cues":[{"time":62040,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":63520,"text":"My wife in high school\nwas a two-time all-state soccer player"},{"time":66920,"text":"and a two-time all-state\nvolleyball player,"},{"time":69240,"text":"and I played \"Dungeons and Dragons.\""},{"time":71280,"text":"And that is why,"},{"time":73400,"text":"although my daughter is an athlete,"},{"time":75360,"text":"she's also a huge nerd, which I love."},{"time":78560,"text":"She walks around our house\nin a cloak of flames"},{"time":81200,"text":"that she made herself."},{"time":83400,"text":"She sits on the Iron Throne --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":85400,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":87200,"text":"even though she has never\nseen \"Game of Thrones,\""},{"time":89560,"text":"primarily because we are not\nthe worst parents who ever lived."},{"time":93440,"text":"But she knows there's someone\ncalled the Mother of Dragons,"},{"time":96240,"text":"and she calls herself that\nand she loves it."},{"time":98360,"text":"She's a huge comic book fan."},{"time":100080,"text":"Right now, her favorite\ncharacter is Groot."},{"time":102160,"text":"She loves Groot."},{"time":103400,"text":"She adores The Incredible Hulk."},{"time":106080,"text":"But my daughter really at heart,"},{"time":108280,"text":"her thing is Star Wars."},{"time":111320,"text":"My kid is a Jedi."},{"time":113560,"text":"Although some days she's also a Sith,"},{"time":115360,"text":"which is a choice that I can respect."}]},{"cues":[{"time":118600,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":119720,"text":"But here's the question\nthat I have to ask."},{"time":122400,"text":"Why is it that when\nmy daughter dresses up,"},{"time":124720,"text":"whether it's Groot or The Incredible Hulk,"},{"time":127320,"text":"whether it's Obi-Wan Kenobi or Darth Maul,"},{"time":130880,"text":"why is every character\nshe dresses up as a boy?"},{"time":136320,"text":"And where are all the female superheroes?"},{"time":138360,"text":"And that is not actually the question,"},{"time":140240,"text":"because there's plenty\nof female superheroes."},{"time":142400,"text":"My question really is,\nwhere is all the female superhero stuff?"},{"time":146640,"text":"Where are the costumes?\nWhere are the toys?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":149600,"text":"Because every day when my daughter\nplays when she dresses up,"},{"time":153360,"text":"she's learning stuff"},{"time":156160,"text":"through a process that,\nin my own line of work,"},{"time":158400,"text":"as a professor of media studies,"},{"time":160000,"text":"we refer to as public pedagogy."},{"time":161960,"text":"That is, it is how societies\nare taught ideologies."},{"time":167200,"text":"It's how you learned what it meant\nto be a man or a woman,"},{"time":169960,"text":"what it meant to behave\nyourself in public,"},{"time":172560,"text":"what it meant to be a patriot\nand have good manners."},{"time":175320,"text":"It's all the constituent social relations\nthat make us up as a people."},{"time":179200,"text":"It's, in short, how we learn\nwhat we know about other people"},{"time":183240,"text":"and about the world."},{"time":185040,"text":"But we live in a 100-percent\nmedia-saturated society."},{"time":189520,"text":"What that means is that every single\naspect of your human existence"},{"time":193040,"text":"outside of your basic bodily functions"},{"time":195440,"text":"is in some way touched by media."},{"time":197920,"text":"From the car that you drive\nto the food that you eat"},{"time":200400,"text":"to the clothes that you wear"},{"time":201800,"text":"to the way you construct\nyour relationships"},{"time":203840,"text":"to the very language\nyou use to formulate thought --"},{"time":206960,"text":"all of that is in some way mediated."},{"time":210240,"text":"So the answer in our society"},{"time":212280,"text":"to how do we learn what we know\nabout other people and about the world"},{"time":215590,"text":"is largely through media."}]},{"cues":[{"time":218880,"text":"Well, there's a wrinkle in that,"},{"time":221040,"text":"in that our society,"},{"time":222840,"text":"media don't simply exist as information\ndistribution technologies and devices."},{"time":228160,"text":"They also exist as corporate entities."},{"time":231040,"text":"And when the distribution of information\nis tied to financial gain,"},{"time":236880,"text":"there's a problem."},{"time":239080,"text":"How big of a problem?"},{"time":240520,"text":"Well think about this:"},{"time":241760,"text":"in 1983, 90 percent of American media\nwere owned by 50 companies."},{"time":248520,"text":"In any market, 50 companies\ndoing something is a lot of companies."},{"time":252840,"text":"It's a lot of different worldviews."},{"time":254720,"text":"In 2015, that number has shrunk to six,"},{"time":259480,"text":"six companies."},{"time":260839,"text":"They are NBCUniversal Comcast,\nAOL Time Warner,"},{"time":264640,"text":"the Walt Disney Company, News Corp,\nViacom and the CBS Corporation."},{"time":270480,"text":"These six companies produce\nnine out of every 10 movies you watch,"},{"time":274480,"text":"nine out of every 10 television shows,\nnine out of every 10 songs,"},{"time":277960,"text":"nine out of every 10 books."},{"time":279760,"text":"So my question to you is,"},{"time":281680,"text":"if six companies control\n90 percent of American media,"},{"time":285400,"text":"how much influence do you think they have\nover what you're allowed to see every day?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":291880,"text":"Because in media studies,"},{"time":293280,"text":"we spend a lot of time saying\nthat media can't tell us what to think,"},{"time":296560,"text":"and they can't; they're terrible at that."},{"time":298840,"text":"But that's not their job."},{"time":300240,"text":"Media don't tell us what to think."},{"time":302200,"text":"Media tell us what to think about."},{"time":305000,"text":"They control the conversation,"},{"time":306880,"text":"and in controlling the conversation,"},{"time":308640,"text":"they don't have to get you\nto think what they want you to think."},{"time":311680,"text":"They'll just get you thinking about\nthe things they want you to think about,"},{"time":315280,"text":"and more importantly, not thinking about\nthings they don't want you to think about."},{"time":319200,"text":"They control the conversation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":321160,"text":"How does this work in practice?"},{"time":322800,"text":"Let's just take one of those companies."},{"time":324800,"text":"We'll do an easy one."},{"time":326040,"text":"Let's talk about the Walt Disney\nCompany for a second."},{"time":328600,"text":"The reason why I always pick\nthe Walt Disney Company is this."},{"time":331520,"text":"Is there a single person in this room\nwho has never seen a Disney movie?"},{"time":334960,"text":"Look around. Exactly."},{"time":337720,"text":"I picked Disney because they have\nwhat we call 100 percent penetration"},{"time":341400,"text":"in our society."},{"time":342640,"text":"Every single person\nhas been exposed to Disney,"},{"time":345040,"text":"so it's an easy one for me to use."},{"time":347040,"text":"Since 1937, Disney has made most\nof its money selling princesses to girls."},{"time":352320,"text":"It's made a huge chunk of its money."},{"time":354440,"text":"Unless, of course, the princess\nyour daughter is interested in,"},{"time":357440,"text":"as my daughter is, is this one."}]},{"cues":[{"time":359880,"text":"See, in 2012,"},{"time":362200,"text":"Disney purchased LucasFilm\nfor the sum of four billion dollars,"},{"time":366840,"text":"and immediately they flooded\nthe Disney stores with Han Solo"},{"time":370680,"text":"and Obi-Wan Kenobi, with Darth Vader\nand Luke Skywalker and Yoda"},{"time":374040,"text":"and not Princess Leia."},{"time":375920,"text":"Why? Because this princess\nmesses up the public pedagogy"},{"time":379360,"text":"for these princesses."},{"time":381160,"text":"So Disney did not put Princess Leia\nmerchandise in the store,"},{"time":384720,"text":"and when people went to Disney and said,"},{"time":386680,"text":"\"Hey, where's all\nthe Princess Leia stuff?\""},{"time":388720,"text":"Disney said, \"We have no intention"},{"time":390400,"text":"of putting Princess Leia\nmerchandise in the store.\""},{"time":392840,"text":"And fans were angry\nand they took to Twitter"},{"time":394960,"text":"with the hashtag #WeWantLeia."},{"time":397080,"text":"And Disney said,\n\"Wait, that's not what we meant."},{"time":399520,"text":"What we meant was,"},{"time":401200,"text":"we don't have any Princess Leia\nmerchandise yet, but we will.\""},{"time":404920,"text":"And that was in 2012, and it is 2015,"},{"time":408320,"text":"and if you go to the Disney Store,\nas I recently have,"},{"time":410876,"text":"and look for Princess Leia merchandise,"},{"time":412765,"text":"do you know how many Princess Leia\nitems there are in the Disney Store?"},{"time":416124,"text":"Zero, because Disney has no intention\nof putting Princess Leia in the store."}]},{"cues":[{"time":419728,"text":"And we shouldn't be surprised\nbecause we found out that was their policy"},{"time":423160,"text":"when they bought Marvel in 2009"},{"time":427160,"text":"for the sum of 4.5 billion dollars."},{"time":430080,"text":"Because when you make a lot of money\nselling princesses to girls,"},{"time":433520,"text":"you also kind of want\nto make money from boys."},{"time":435920,"text":"And so what better to sell boys\nthan superheroes?"},{"time":438400,"text":"So now Disney had access\nto Captain America and to Thor,"},{"time":441400,"text":"The Incredible Hulk,"},{"time":442760,"text":"and they had access even"},{"time":445560,"text":"to a group of superheroes\nno one had ever even heard of."},{"time":448320,"text":"That's how good Marvel was\nat selling superheroes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":451480,"text":"Last year, they released a film\ncalled \"Guardians of the Galaxy.\""},{"time":454920,"text":"It's a film that absolutely\nshould not work."},{"time":457840,"text":"Nobody knew who they were\nexcept for comic book nerds like me."},{"time":461680,"text":"One of the characters is a talking tree."},{"time":464000,"text":"One of the characters\nis an anthropomorphic raccoon."},{"time":466480,"text":"It should not work."},{"time":467960,"text":"And they made a killing\noff of \"Guardians of the Galaxy.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":471160,"text":"This character here in the middle,\nher name is Gamora."},{"time":473720,"text":"She's played by Zoe Saldana,"},{"time":475600,"text":"and she is strong and smart and fast\nand fights like a ninja,"},{"time":479280,"text":"and she is played\nby a beautiful black woman,"},{"time":481440,"text":"and my daughter fell in love with her."},{"time":483640,"text":"So like any good nerd dad,\nI went to buy my daughter Gamora stuff,"},{"time":487880,"text":"and when I got to the store,\nI learned a very interesting thing."},{"time":491000,"text":"If I wanted to buy her a Gamora backpack,"},{"time":493760,"text":"well, Gamora's not on it."},{"time":496240,"text":"They probably should have marketed this\nas \"some\" of the Guardians of the Galaxy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":500080,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":502160,"text":"And if I wanted to buy her a lunchbox,\nshe wasn't on it,"},{"time":505160,"text":"and if I wanted to buy her a t-shirt,"},{"time":507160,"text":"she wasn't on it."},{"time":508560,"text":"And as a matter of fact,"},{"time":510480,"text":"if I went to the store, as I did,"},{"time":512720,"text":"and looked at the display,"},{"time":514240,"text":"you would find a small picture\nof Gamora right here,"},{"time":517080,"text":"but if you look at any\nof the actual merchandise on that shelf,"},{"time":520840,"text":"Gamora is not on any of it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":523440,"text":"Now, I could have taken to Twitter\nwith the hashtag #WheresGamora,"},{"time":527120,"text":"like millions of fans did\nacross the world,"},{"time":530320,"text":"but the truth was\nI wasn't even really that surprised,"},{"time":534440,"text":"because I was there\nwhen Disney had released \"The Avengers.\""},{"time":538400,"text":"And just this year, we got\na new Avengers movie, the \"Age of Ultron,\""},{"time":541760,"text":"and we were very excited,"},{"time":543000,"text":"because there was not one\nbut two female superheroes,"},{"time":545520,"text":"Scarlet Witch and Black Widow."},{"time":547520,"text":"And we were very excited."},{"time":548840,"text":"But here's the real thing about this."},{"time":551080,"text":"Even though Scarlett Johansson,"},{"time":552880,"text":"who is one of the most popular\nactresses in America, plays Black Widow,"},{"time":556360,"text":"and Black Widow is the star"},{"time":557720,"text":"of not one, not two,\nbut five different Marvel movies,"},{"time":562720,"text":"there is not a single piece\nof Black Widow merchandise available."},{"time":567360,"text":"Not one."},{"time":568760,"text":"And if you go to the Disney store\nand look for a Black Widow costume,"},{"time":572040,"text":"what you will find, is you will find\nCaptain America and The Incredible Hulk."},{"time":575680,"text":"You will find Iron Man and Thor."},{"time":577280,"text":"You will even find War Machine,"},{"time":578800,"text":"who isn't even really\nin the movie that long."},{"time":581600,"text":"Who you will not find is Black Widow."},{"time":584040,"text":"And I could have gone to Twitter\nwith the hashtag, as many people did,"},{"time":587600,"text":"# WheresNatasha."},{"time":589400,"text":"But I'm tired of doing that."},{"time":591760,"text":"I'm tired of having to do that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":593560,"text":"All over the country right now,"},{"time":595120,"text":"there are kids playing\nwith the Cycle Blast Quinjet play set,"},{"time":598600,"text":"where Captain America\nrides a motorcycle out of a moving jet"},{"time":602600,"text":"and it's really awesome."},{"time":604160,"text":"You know how awesome it is?"},{"time":605520,"text":"So awesome that when\nit happened in the movie,"},{"time":608000,"text":"it was Black Widow that did it."},{"time":610400,"text":"Not only has she been erased,"},{"time":614000,"text":"but she has been replaced\nwith a male figure."}]},{"cues":[{"time":619640,"text":"And so what is this teaching us?"},{"time":622720,"text":"I mean, over the next five years,"},{"time":624640,"text":"Disney and Warner Bros.\nand a bunch of movie studios"},{"time":628360,"text":"are going to release\nover 30 feature-length films"},{"time":631800,"text":"with comic book characters,"},{"time":633280,"text":"and of those 30 feature-length films,"},{"time":635680,"text":"exactly two of them\nwill have female solo leads."},{"time":640600,"text":"Two."},{"time":641840,"text":"Now, there will be females\nin the rest of these movies,"},{"time":644720,"text":"but they will be sidekicks,\nthey will be love interests,"},{"time":647400,"text":"they will be members of teams."},{"time":648853,"text":"They will not be the main character."},{"time":650680,"text":"And if what we learn, what we know"},{"time":652960,"text":"about other people and about the world\nwe learn through media,"},{"time":656000,"text":"then these companies are teaching\nmy daughter that even if she is strong"},{"time":659560,"text":"and smart and fast\nand fights like a ninja,"},{"time":662800,"text":"all four of which are true of her,"},{"time":665880,"text":"it doesn't matter."},{"time":667640,"text":"She will either be ignored like Gamora"},{"time":670080,"text":"or erased and replaced with a boy"},{"time":672760,"text":"like Black Widow."},{"time":674920,"text":"And it's not fair."},{"time":676600,"text":"It's not fair to her and it's not fair\nto your sons and daughters either."}]},{"cues":[{"time":680680,"text":"But here's the thing:"},{"time":681960,"text":"I'm raising a little girl,\nand she has a little tomboy in her,"},{"time":685280,"text":"which by the way is\na terrible thing to call a girl."},{"time":687800,"text":"What that basically is saying is,\nthose traits that define you,"},{"time":691040,"text":"they're not really yours,"},{"time":692280,"text":"they're just on loan to you\nfor a little while from boys."},{"time":695560,"text":"But do you know how much grief\nshe's going to take in her life"},{"time":698880,"text":"for having a little tomboy in her?"},{"time":701320,"text":"Zero. None."},{"time":703320,"text":"People will think it's cute."},{"time":704720,"text":"They'll call her feisty,\nbecause in our society,"},{"time":707360,"text":"adding so-called male traits to girls"},{"time":709800,"text":"is seen as an upgrade, seen as a bonus."},{"time":713000,"text":"I'm not raising a little boy, like Mike."}]},{"cues":[{"time":716400,"text":"Mike is a little boy in Florida.\nHe's 11 years old,"},{"time":719360,"text":"and the thing that he loves\nmost in the world"},{"time":721520,"text":"is a show called \"My Little Pony:\nFriendship is Magic,\""},{"time":724480,"text":"like millions of other children\nacross America."},{"time":727560,"text":"Now, the show is marketed to girls\nages five to nine,"},{"time":731080,"text":"but there are millions of boys"},{"time":733440,"text":"and grown men"},{"time":735240,"text":"who enjoy \"My Little Pony:\nFriendship is Magic.\""},{"time":737640,"text":"They have a club."},{"time":738880,"text":"They call themselves Bronies,"},{"time":740760,"text":"pony bros, guys who like ponies."},{"time":744000,"text":"I happen to be one of them."},{"time":745920,"text":"And what are Mike and myself"},{"time":749480,"text":"and millions of other boys and men\nlearning in this feminine,"},{"time":752362,"text":"sissified world of \"My Little Pony?\""},{"time":755240,"text":"Well, they're learning to study hard\nand to work hard and to party hard"},{"time":760120,"text":"and to look good and to feel good"},{"time":762200,"text":"and to do good,"},{"time":763760,"text":"and heaven preserve us from teaching\nthese wussified concepts to boys."}]},{"cues":[{"time":768880,"text":"So the other kids in his neighborhood\npick on Mike and they beat him up"},{"time":772840,"text":"and they make fun of him,"},{"time":774120,"text":"and at 11 years old, Mike goes home,"},{"time":776600,"text":"finds a belt, wraps it around his neck,"},{"time":778960,"text":"and hangs himself\nfrom the top bunk of his bed."},{"time":781760,"text":"Because we have developed a society"},{"time":784360,"text":"in which you would rather be dead as a boy\nthan thought of as liking stuff for girls."},{"time":790280,"text":"And that is not Mike's fault.\nThat is our fault."},{"time":793480,"text":"We have failed him."},{"time":795800,"text":"We have failed our children."},{"time":798120,"text":"And we have to do better for them."},{"time":800080,"text":"We have to stop making it\nso that the only female superheroes"},{"time":803000,"text":"appear on shirts that are pink\nand cut for girls."},{"time":806840,"text":"We have to stop."}]},{"cues":[{"time":808080,"text":"And when I was putting this together,\npeople said to me,"},{"time":810920,"text":"\"Well, that's never going to happen.\"\nAnd I said, \"Oh really?\""},{"time":813880,"text":"Because just this year, Target announced"},{"time":815840,"text":"that they were going to stop\ngendering their toy aisles."},{"time":819200,"text":"They were going to mix it up."},{"time":820640,"text":"Now, before we break our shoulders\npatting Target on the back,"},{"time":824240,"text":"just this week they released a shirt"},{"time":826200,"text":"in which one of the most\niconic scenes in \"Star Wars: A New Hope\""},{"time":829440,"text":"where Princess Leia stands up\nto the Dark Lord of the Sith,"},{"time":832440,"text":"was released on a t-shirt"},{"time":833680,"text":"in which she's mysteriously\nreplaced by Luke."},{"time":835960,"text":"So let's don't pat ourselves\non the back too much."},{"time":839000,"text":"Just this week also,"},{"time":840520,"text":"Disney announced it was no longer\ngoing to gender its Halloween costumes,"},{"time":845000,"text":"which I say, \"Thank you, Disney,"},{"time":846800,"text":"except the only costumes you make\nare of male superheroes,"},{"time":849560,"text":"so does it matter\nwho you have wearing them?\""},{"time":853040,"text":"Just this week, Mattel, who makes Barbie,"},{"time":855280,"text":"announced they're going to release\na line of DC superhero girls."},{"time":858760,"text":"And the funny thing is,"},{"time":860040,"text":"they met with girls"},{"time":861480,"text":"and asked them what they\nwanted to see in dolls,"},{"time":863880,"text":"and you can see, they have calves"},{"time":866280,"text":"and elbows that bend\nso they can do superhero stuff."},{"time":869880,"text":"And please buy them."},{"time":871440,"text":"And don't just buy them\nfor your daughters,"},{"time":873480,"text":"buy them for your sons."},{"time":874840,"text":"Because it's important that boys\nplay with and as female superheroes"},{"time":879800,"text":"just as my daughter plays\nwith and as male superheroes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":883800,"text":"As a matter of fact, what I would love"},{"time":885680,"text":"is a world in which every person\nwho goes to the store"},{"time":888280,"text":"goes with a little flowchart in their head"},{"time":891000,"text":"of whether or not they should buy\nthis toy for a boy or a girl,"},{"time":894120,"text":"and it's a real simple flowchart\nbecause it only has one question on it."},{"time":897525,"text":"It says, \"Is this toy\noperated with your genitals?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":900600,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":902880,"text":"If the answer is yes,"},{"time":905800,"text":"then that is not a toy for children."}]},{"cues":[{"time":907640,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":910760,"text":"And if the answer is no,"},{"time":913960,"text":"then it's for boys and girls."},{"time":916200,"text":"It's really simple."},{"time":917720,"text":"Because today is about the future\nof the future, and in my future,"},{"time":921720,"text":"boys and girls are equally respected,"},{"time":925000,"text":"equally valued, and most importantly,\nequally represented."}]},{"cues":[{"time":930520,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":931760,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}